{"tid":1673723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【10月尾】日本TV節目再講香港局勢最新發展","createTime":"2019-10-24T22:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T01:19:56.000Z","uid":202464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5479fda28ce2e78e35e4564dad535f2ada94ba17","tid":1673723,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T22:53:48.000Z","msg":"TBS電視台既晨早清談節目『ひるおび!』（英文:HIRUOBI!）唔止第一次詳解香港局勢。<br />\n<br />\n佢地7月尾已經分析過7.21元朗白衣人同支那辦/特區政府關系密切。<br />\n<br />\n前幾日又發功，講返10月香港最新形勢：<br />\n<br />\n原片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bYjkRxa7U1c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbYjkRxa7U1c&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=4712fa55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bYjkRxa7U1c</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文字：<br />\n<br />\n1. 解釋返香港反送中運動嘅因由、五大訴求係乜<br />\n<br />\n2. 點解政府「撤回」之後香港人都仲要上街、政府嘅處理手法等等<br />\n<br />\n3. 引述英國金融時報，支那想換走Carrie；然後引述返支那外交部話冇呢件事<br />\n<br />\n4.  陳同佳放監、台港政治角力、管政協既背景引起台灣疑慮<br />\n<br />\n5.  話香港有網民同報紙發現Carrie係日皇登基儀式玩電話，有意見認為呢種行為係「極度咁挑戰國際儀式典禮上禮儀」、然後又引述返Carrie話典禮上面冇禁止玩電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識日文既文宣，請盡情twitter出去"},{"pid":"56c7381f28b7249cb384021bc65d760cd0d5e284","tid":1673723,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T23:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f0ae1bbe7e63711063cfccfc55633af93e7172","tid":1673723,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T23:18:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatorleahy/status/1184865122977746945?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatorleahy%2Fstatus%2F1184865122977746945%3Fs%3D21&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=44012d11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatorleahy%2Fstatus%2F1184865122977746945%3Fs%3D21&h=1ba2513b\" da